body:
I have no objection to adding this to getnetworkinfo, but just noting that [jq](https://stedolan.github.io/jq/) is your friend here:

```
bitcoin-cli getpeerinfo | jq "group_by(.inbound) | map({Inbound: .[0].inbound, Count: length}) | .[]"
{
  "Inbound": false,
  "Count": 9
}
{
  "Inbound": true,
  "Count": 6
}
```
